cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper proposes an approach for next frame prediction in video using transformations, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The approach is unsupervised and uses a smaller prediction model, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also proposes a new evaluation protocol for video frame prediction models, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or neural networks (cs.NE).
